data.description: Welcome to this incredible home that is sure to impress from the moment you arrive. Upon entering, instantly notice all of the sunlight streaming in and welcoming you inside. The beautiful kitchen features vaulted ceilings, 42" cabinets, stainless steel appliances, Corian countertops, a ceiling fan and an eating area. The space opens effortlessly into the sun-drenched family room that boasts gleaming hardwood floors, vaulted ceilings, 2 large skylights, a ceiling fan and a cozy gas fireplace. The 3 bedrooms all feature rich hardwood floors and have ceiling fans as well. The fantastic master has a private en suite bathroom and a sliding glass door that leads out to the deck and fenced-in backyard. A second full bathroom completes the main level. The unfinished basement is HUGE and has a washer and dryer. Endless possibilities to transform this lower level into even more exceptional living space. All it needs is your finishing touches! TONS of updates including: brand new driveway, roof, updated light fixtures, new flooring, furnace/AC, newer stainless steel appliances, washer, dryer, pressure tank and MUCH MORE! A perfect location near endless shopping, dining, entertainment, parks, golf and top-rated Lake Zurich schools. Enjoy all that Forest Lake has to offer! Community center, numerous parks, lake rights to fish and boat on the 42 acre lake or just relax on the numerous beaches! Don't let this exceptional opportunity get away!
